{"tid":695025,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"針對華人移民 全美湧現「大使館」電話騙案","createTime":"2018-06-09T01:30:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-09T03:11:13.000Z","uid":14918,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"dc067f49123384d8d7760ea30419f8687610d366","tid":695025,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T01:30:27.000Z","msg":"美國全國出現針對操普通話人士的電話騙案，有受害人表示，收到謊稱是中國大使館人員來電，被騙去數百萬美元。美國和中國政府已呼籲華人提高警覺。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n這些說普通話的電話錄音，部分假冒由中國大使館發出，聲稱扣起了居民的文件或包裹，要求匯款贖回。紐約市警方表示，單在紐約自去年12月起，已有21名中國移民，至少被騙去250萬元。<br />\r\n騙徒利用假冒電話號碼，以相同地理位置的區號，來減低受害人警覺性。今年頭五個月，美國聯邦通訊委員會，收到數百宗類似電話投訴，數量較去年倍增。<br />\n\r<br />\n中國駐美大使館、聯邦貿易委員會、紐約及洛杉磯警方，皆分別發出通告，呼籲民眾若收到說普通話的錄音電話，應馬上掛斷；若曾按照吩咐匯款給致電方，應與警方聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n雖遠必諸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91fb55f6c70cce0f72f9d8a68d71b01287dee058","tid":695025,"uid":113178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T01:32:45.000Z","msg":"蝦自己人最叻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c91aaf42035d83902f033b3c523efc5713a16d29","tid":695025,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T01:33:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70e36482e3a33fc438cee824753129ee5ecced74","tid":695025,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T01:35:07.000Z","msg":"加拿大都好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0a24fc9bff262c3ad98748d258cafe370e2a4d3","tid":695025,"uid":20414,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T01:38:08.000Z","msg":"澳洲都勁多啦<br />\n一開波話中國領事館已經知咩事<br 